import selectImg from '../../images/svg-1.svg' 
 import img_2 from '../../images/recycle-icon.svg'

      buttonLabel: 'Get Started',
      underline: true,
      bg_container: 'container',
      img: selectImg,
      alt: 'bottle'

  export const homeObjTwo = {
    description: "Plastic waste is currently making a huge impact in our world. From its production proccess to its after use waste. WasteConnect's mission is to create an opportunity for the wastes to be used in different sector of manufacturing. ",
    imgStart: 'start',
    headline: 'Our Mission',
    underline: false,
    vis: 'btn--disable',
    bg_container: 'bg-lightblue',
    img: img_2,
    alt: 'recycle'
};
